sectionNotes: Restricted to students with Junior, Senior, or Graduate class standing. Restricted to BS:Fd Sci & Hmn Nutrn-FS -UIUC, MS:FSci &Hmn Nutrition -UIUC, PHD:FSci &Hmn Nutrition -UIUC, or MS: Food Sc Hum N - PSM -UIUC.
sectionText: Restricted to FSHN undergraduate and graduate students only until after junior registration.  Remaining seats will be released to the general student population when sophomore registration opens.  If you get a 'course full' error message and want to be added to a wait list for this class, go to www.fshn.illinois.edu and click on Current Students then Waitlist Information. Wait lists will not open until one week before classes start in January.
